title: Jimi Hendrix - The Video Experience
description:
Jimi Hendrix
The Video Experience
Multiple Sources including AUD shot video and PRO shot video

Includes:

Newport Pop Festival 1969
New York Rock Festival 1968
Rainbow Bridge Vibratory Colr-Sound Experiment 1970
"Top of The Pops" TV broadcast
"Popside" TV broadcast
"Happening For Lulu" TV broadcast
plus Promotional Videos


Video Codec: Mpeg2
Video Bitrate: 5283kbps 
Video System: NTSC Color = B&W @ 29.970f/sec
Audio Codec: AC3
Audio Bitrate: 192kb/s


Artwork is included

The artwork has the proper information and order of performances with rthe exception of th BOG performance at Fillmore East which would not transfer. Everything else is here. 
Enjoy
